cu.explanation_en: Setting the S1-U port to 0 will cause GTP-U tunnel establishment failure and prevent user plane data transmission.

du.explanation_en: Setting absolute frequency SSB to a negative value (-1) will cause SSB transmission errors and prevent UE cell search and synchronization.
du.explanation_zh: 將 SSB 絕對頻率設定為負值 (-1)，會導致 SSB 傳輸錯誤，並阻止 UE 細胞搜尋和同步。
